title: 'Wherever you are send us some signal' - Family's plea to missing rapper Theophilus London
description: The family of rapper Theophilus London have filed a missing persons report and are asking for the public's help, saying he has not been seen in months.

title: Brazilian football icon Pele has died
description: Brazilian football star Pele has died at the age of 82, his agent has confirmed.

title: Bob Marley's grandson, Joseph 'Jo Mersa' Marley, dies aged 31
description: Bob Marley's grandson, Joseph 'Jo Mersa' Marley, has died aged 31.

title: 'Not enough beds': Doctors describe chaos in hospitals as COVID sweeps across China
description: Doctors in China have described the chaos unfolding within hospitals as COVID-19 infections sweep the country.

title: Pope Francis asks for prayers for his predecessor Pope Benedict and says he is 'very sick'
description: Pope Francis has asked for prayers for his predecessor Pope Benedict saying the former head of the Catholic Church is "very sick".

title: COVID patients no longer have to quarantine in Hong Kong as restrictions are lifted
description: People who test positive for coronavirus will no longer have to quarantine in Hong Kong as part of a lifting of restrictions, the Chinese territory's leader has said.

title: Two teenage boys charged with murder of British mother-of-two in Australia
description: Two teenage boys have been charged with the murder of a British mother-of-two who was killed while defending her home in Australia on Boxing Day.
